timelineItems.name: Kasey Hunter
timelineItems.text: Nothing against the Dynamo but you know your supporter culture is struggling when you require a full orchestra to play for 90mins. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.name: Houston Dynamo
timelineItems.text: 13' Manneh with a run from midfield, but the Dynamo close him down in the box before he can get a shot on goal. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.name: Tim Donahoe
timelineItems.text: #HOUvVAN #ForeverOrange record for most off sides calls on one team in an MLS game?

timelineItems.name: Simon Fudge
timelineItems.text: Awful from Ricardo Clark, with space and time to strike... #HOUvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.desc: The Vancouver Whitecaps take their league best points-per-game to Houston as the Dynamo push desperately for the playoffs.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: Houston Dynamo vs. Vancouver Whitecaps | August 29, 2015

timelineItems.name: Houston Dynamo
timelineItems.text: 2' First one is cleared out but the Dynamo regain possession, and Barnes has a cross go out for another corner. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.name: Kasey Hunter
timelineItems.text: Manneh so dangerous. Almost to the point that you can notch him for at least one road goal per match. #VWFC

timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Darren Mattocks (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) right footed shot from the center of the box is saved in the center of the goal.
timelineItems.title: CHANCE: Kekuta Manneh plays a lovely through ball to Darren Mattocks, whose shot is blocked

timelineItems.name: Houston Dynamo
timelineItems.text: 24' SUB: Luis Garrido enters for DaMarcus Beasley, who has been hobbling for the last few minutes. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.name: Matthew Doyle
timelineItems.text: DaMarcus Beasley comes off injured. Doubt we see him in red, white and blue for the next couple of friendlies. #HOUvVAN #USMNT

timelineItems.name: Lou Roesch
timelineItems.text: Beasley not lasting long in his return to the starting line-up #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.name: Simon Fudge
timelineItems.text: Coyle forced into taking veteran Beasley out at left back. Garrido replaces him... #HOUvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: Houston Dynamo
timelineItems.text: 25' Big time save from Deric! Manneh plays Mattocks behind the defense but Deric closes down and blocks the shot. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Matias Laba (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) is shown the yellow card for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: YELLOW CARD: Matias Laba is booked after a professional foul on Giles Barnes

timelineItems.name: Houston Dynamo
timelineItems.text: 27' Yellow card issued to Matias Laba for chopping down Barnes from behind on a break. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.name: Houston Dynamo
timelineItems.text: Garrido moves to the middle of the park with Clark, Alex shifts to left back after the sub. #HOUvVAN

timelineItems.name: AsianAdidasGirl

timelineItems.text: Tim Parker continues to look like a guy who should figure for the US u-23s in Olympic qualifying. Smooth, reads the game fast. #HOUvVAN
